{"tid":100373,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【李波翻版？】明鏡：傳留港富豪年三十遭押返中國","createTime":"2017-01-30T03:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-30T11:22:43.000Z","uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"133eb3331d5b935ca04446e151a97d779d9a75b6","tid":100373,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:28:29.000Z","msg":"2017-01-30 08:40:00 HKT<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n海外媒體明鏡廣播電台報道，一名控制資產達萬億的中國超級富豪，於年三十深夜在香港被數十名公安、國安人員抓捕，押返內地。事件如屬實，將成為去年銅鑼灣書店股東李波遭中共派人跨境執法的翻版，嚴重破壞一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n明鏡廣播電台指，中共突控制該名富豪，是擔心他如另一名富豪郭文貴向揭露內地貪官。據悉，該名被控制的富豪打理資產數以萬億人民幣，涉及多個中共頂尖家族。該名超級富豪被帶走時，身邊有八名保鏢。而明鏡新聞網表示網頁被黑客攻擊，直至今早仍未恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n報道指有關消息未有得到中共官方消息證實，但消息來說指出，有指行動不單有利於習近平清除十九大障礙，也是可能是另一次更大反貪行動的開始。<br />\n<br />\n明鏡廣播電台/明鏡新聞網"},{"pid":"b8c0088a10e5c473331b19f65aa76cd0e02b82af","tid":100373,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:28:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170130&amp;guid=56239782&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170130%26guid%3D56239782%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=WPS43JJkpORccPZf4osG%2FbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=9bfccfe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170130%26guid%3D56239782%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=44f6a28d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170130&amp;guid=56239782&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"e84820ec830569ddad6f4b7424eaaff78c1f0471","tid":100373,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T03:30:12.000Z","msg":"香港真係變左Casablanca <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0ca3e2e4346279d0c394e1cb5e5066c866bc3a","tid":100373,"